\c 28
\s Efuremu naJudha vanotsiurwa
\p
\v 1 Nhamo kukorona yekuzvikudza yezvidhakwa zvekwaEfuremu, nekuruva rinobvuruvara rerunako rwekubwinya kwake, riri pamusoro pemusoro wemupata wakaorera kwazvo, wevakarohwa newaini.
\v 2 Tarirai, Ishe ane simba uye wakagwinya. Achakanda panyika neruoko, sedutu remhepo rine mvura rechimvuramabwe, dutu rinoparadza, semafashame emvura zhinji ane simba anokukura.
\v 3 Korona yekuzvikudza yezvidhakwa zvekwaEfuremu ichatsikirwa pasi netsoka.
\v 4 Uye ruva rinobvuruvara rerunako rwekubwinya kwake riri pamusoro pemusoro wemupata wakaorera kwazvo richava sechibereko chekutanga zhizha risati rasvika, kuti muoni waro aone, richiri muruoko rwake arimedze.
\p
\v 5 Nezuva iro Jehovha wedzihondo achava korona yekubwinya, neukomba hwerunako kuna vakasara vevanhu vake,
\v 6 nemweya wemutongo kune agere pamutongo, nesimba kune avo vanodzosera hondo kusuwo.
\v 7 Uyewo ava vakarasika nekuda kwewaini, uye nekuda kwezvinodhaka vakatsauka; mupristi nemuporofita vanorasika nekuda kwezvinodhaka, vakamedzwa newaini, vakatsauka nekuda kwezvinodhaka, vanorasika pakuona, vanogumburwa pamutongo.
\v 8 Nokuti matafura ese azere nemarutsi \add ne\add*kusviba; hapana nzvimbo \add yakanaka\add*.
\p
\v 9 Ndiani waachadzidzisa ruzivo? Uye ndiani waachaita anzwisise shoko? Vakarumurwa pamukaka; vakabviswa pamazamu.
\v 10 Nokuti mutemo uri pamusoro pemutemo, mutemo pamusoro pemutemo, chirevo pamusoro pechirevo, chirevo pamusoro pechirevo, apa zvishoma, apo zvishoma.
\v 11 Nokuti nemiromo inonyomba, uye nerwumwe rurimi anotaura kuvanhu ava,
\v 12 vaakati kwavari: Iri izororo, zorodzayi vakaneta, uye uku kuvandudzwa. Asi havana kuda kunzwa.
\v 13 Asi shoko raJehovha raiva kwavari mutemo pamusoro pemutemo, mutemo pamusoro pemutemo, chirevo pamusoro pechirevo, chirevo pamusoro pechirevo, apa zvishoma, apo zvishoma; kuti vaende, vawe nenhendashure, vavhunike, vateyewe, vatapwe.
\p
\v 14 Naizvozvo inzwai shoko raJehovha, imwi vanhu vekunyomba munotonga vanhu ava vari muJerusarema.
\v 15 Nokuti makati: Takaita sungano nerufu, uye negehena takaita chibvumirano, panopfuura shamhu inofashamira, haisviki kwatiri, nokuti takaita nhema dzive utiziro hwedu, takavanda pasi peunyengeri.
\v 16 Naizvozvo anoreva Ishe Jehovha: Tarirai, ndinoisa paZiyoni ibwe rive nheyo, ibwe rakaedzwa, ibwe repakona rinokosha, nheyo yakasimba; anotenda haakurumidzi.
\v 17 Ndichaisa mutongo uve rwodzi rwekuyera, uye kururama kuve chekururamisa. Zvino chimvuramabwe chichakukura utiziro hwenhema, uye mvura zhinji ichakukura nzvimbo yekuvanda.
\v 18 Zvino sungano yenyu nerufu ichadzimwa, nechitenderano chenyu negehena hachingamiri, shamhu inofashamira painopfuura, ipapo muchatsikirwa pasi nayo.
\v 19 Kubva panguva yekupfuura kwayo, ichakutorai; nokuti kuedze nekuedza ichapfuura, masikati neusiku; uye chichava chityiso kunzwisisa shoko koga.
\v 20 Nokuti mubhedha uchava mupfupisa kuti \add munhu\add* atandavare, nejira richava dikisa kuti \add munhu\add* azvimonere.
\v 21 Nokuti Jehovha achasimuka se\add pa\add*gomo rePerazimi, achatsamwa se\add pa\add*mupata weGibhiyoni; kuti aite basa rake, basa rake risina kujairika, aite chiito chake, chiito chake chisina kujairika.
\v 22 Naizvozvo regai kunyomba, zvimwe zvisungo zvenyu zvisimbiswe; nokuti ndakanzwa kuna Ishe Jehovha wedzihondo kupedzwa kwatemwa pamusoro penyika yese.
\p
\v 23 Ipai nzeve, mugonzwa inzwi rangu, teererai, mugonzwa kureva kwangu.
\v 24 Zuva rese murimi anorimira kudzvara here? Anozarura nekuputsa mavhinga ivhu rake here?
\v 25 Hazvina kudaro here, aenzanisa chiso chawo, kuti akushe kumini tema, nekukusha kumini, nekuisa gorosi rakanaka mumisara, nebhari yakatarwa, ne\add sipereti\add* kumativi awo here?
\v 26 Nokuti Mwari wake anomuzivisa nenzira, agomudzidzisa.
\v 27 Nokuti kumini tema haipurwi nemupuro unopinza, nevhiri rengoro harikunguruswi pamusoro pekumini; asi kumini tema inopurwa netsvimbo, nekumini neshamhu.
\v 28 \add Zviyo\add* zvechingwa zvinokuyiwa, nokuti haangarambi achingozvipura; kuapwanya nevhiri rengoro yake, uye haangaakuyi nemabhiza ake.
\p
\v 29 Neizvi zvinobva kuna Jehovha wedzihondo, anoshamisa pakupa mazano, mukuru pakushanda \add kwake\add*.